responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "C9B918D942278A5E30698D96A3282B55", "So she has fallen, yet her blight upon the citdel remains. She must have been cast into her former prison rather then Duzahk. We shall wait and see if it disipates. Only then can I be sure she has been sent back to her prison.")
